title: President Biden Announces Presidential Delegation to the Republic of The Gambia to Attend Presidential Inauguration of His Excellency Adama Barrow | The White House
content: President Joseph R. Biden, Jr. today announced the designation of a Presidential Delegation to Banjul, The Gambia to attend the Inauguration of His Excellency Adama Barrow on January 19, 2022.The Honorable Richard Carlton Paschall III, United States Ambassador to The Gambia, will lead the delegation.###
